separating each list into cards

00:27:19.490 --> 00:27:22.090
adds unnecessary visual
noise, and it also

00:27:22.090 --> 00:27:26.310
makes it very difficult to
scan the content quickly.

00:27:26.310 --> 00:27:28.740
