interaction cues,

00:27:28.740 --> 00:27:31.700
like how things are going to
move and interact in a space.

00:27:31.700 --> 00:27:34.070
For example, the peeking
surface in the calculator

00:27:34.070 --> 00:27:36.600
is a hint to the user that
they can be pulled out

00:27:36.600 --> 00:27:38.300
to reveal something
new or different

00:27:38.300 --> 00:27:42.020
