00:27:49.090 --> 00:27:50.840
so you guys can use
them when you guys are

00:27:50.840 --> 00:27:52.090
designing your app.

00:27:52.090 --> 00:27:54.900
These layout structures
used a consistent approach

00:27:54.900 --> 00:27:58.100
that I mentioned today about
surface layers and shadows.

00:27:58.100 --> 00:28:01.320
